{"tid":1925343,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"祖記先開紀錄，之後森多利亞中5人反cup,費倫天拿最新連中3人迫近榜首。。","createTime":"2020-03-14T10:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T11:47:09.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d9e3f0ee2a7f6bc52547f8b825f28a57e22d120f","tid":1925343,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T10:16:36.000Z","msg":"香港時間3月14日下午，意甲費倫天拿球會官方宣佈，兩名球員古杜尼和佩澤拉新型冠狀病毒檢測結果為陽性，另外球隊的理療師斯特凡諾-達伊內利也感染了新冠病毒。三人表現出了一些症狀，因此接受了檢測，結果均為陽性。三人目前健康狀況良好，待在費倫天拿的家中。<br />\n<br />\n  截至目前，感染新型冠狀病毒的意甲球員已經達到9人，其中森多利亞5人，費倫天拿3人，祖雲達斯1人。這9名球員分別是：<br />\n<br />\n  森多利亞：加比亞甸尼，科萊，艾賓艾卡度，拉古米拿，托爾斯比；<br />\n<br />\n  費倫天拿：弗拉賀維奇，古杜尼，佩澤拉；<br />\n<br />\n  祖雲達斯：魯加尼。"},{"pid":"579272b3cc3689fd0f5cbb35bb7952489b125196","tid":1925343,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T10:17:17.000Z","msg":"意甲無啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d7879ce26d169643374f2b731544d7fef776c8","tid":1925343,"uid":129044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"C朗唔係中咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8bbab94cbbb9decf88e7e816ecf9c8b798210d1","tid":1925343,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T10:26:18.000Z","msg":"費倫隊長都中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c21c597d28f5b8215cf9fd09d656bd22dac2c7","tid":1925343,"uid":192824,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T10:26:45.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pxUT0MY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpxUT0MY.jpg&h=3edea54b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eg2Kn0j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feg2Kn0j.jpg&h=830ff7c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95ebe98c7b2e